name: Rainbow Rangers
overview: Rainbow Rangers takes place in the magical land of Kaleidoscopia and focuses on the adventures of seven 9-year-old girlsâ€”Rosie Redd, Bonnie Blueberry, Indigo Allfruit, Anna Banana, Mandarin Orange, Pepper Mintz, and Lavender Laviolette- who are all represented by the colors of the rainbow. Each use their own powers to help protect the citizens of their land, clean the planet, and make the world a better place.

episodes.name: Go With the Rainbow Floe
episodes.overview: The Rangers save a baby polar bear stranded on an ice floe.

episodes.name: Northern Lights
episodes.overview: Rosie, Anna, and Mandy lose their Spectra Scooters while helping a seal family in Lake Saima and discover the northern lights, though Anna insists at finishing quickly, as since she is afraid of the dark she doesn't want to stay until nighttime.

episodes.name: Monarch Migration
episodes.overview: Pepper, Anna, and Indigo help a kaleidoscope of butterflies migrate to their new home in Mexico by building a storm shelter for them, but they also have the hurry before any more bad weather hits

episodes.name: That Sinking Feeling
episodes.overview: Rosie, Anna, and Pepper help a mother horse who's fallen into a sinkhole. Pepper, however, is afraid of tight and small spaces, and is reluctant to get in the particularly cramped area with the mare, especially after the other 2 rangers fall in the pit.

episodes.name: Tree Hugger
episodes.overview: Rosie, B.B., and Lavender help save a forest from deforestation at Preston Praxton's nefarious hands, though their efforts to stop his plan at constructing a water park are hampered when he traps them in a front end loader rigged as a booby trap

episodes.name: Turtle in a Net
episodes.overview: B.B., Indigo, and Rosie have to save a sea turtle caught in a fishing net, but the net turns out to be from a shrimping boat owned by Preston Praxton, and he strands them below the waves to keep them out of his way.

episodes.name: Sludge Stream
episodes.overview: Rosie, Pepper, and Indigo have to stop a sludge stream from flowing, additionally they have to stop a boy from coming to harm from touching the industrial waste. They find the sludge to be coming from one of Preston Praxton's factory sites, and their two-part plan quickly comes into trouble.

episodes.name: The Tsunami
episodes.overview: B.B., Anna, and Mandy try save Preston and Patty from a tsunami. But Preston, wanting the whole beach to himself, refuses to leave and places everyone left in grave danger, even more so when he begins following treasure instead of the rangers' instructions.

episodes.name: When Beetles Bark
episodes.overview: Lavender, Rosie, and Anna save a bear's home in Montana from beetles that feed on tree bark, but afraid of all bugs Lavender is extremely reluctant to help out when she has to act as a speaker for the beetles on the rangers' behalf. Upon being rounded up as their queen, however, she almost jeopardizes their mission.

episodes.name: Pollution Island
episodes.overview: Indigo, Mandy, and B.B. help a hermit crab that's stuck in a lotion container from dying of chemical poisoning. Indigo is very determined to finish their mission and leave the polluted beach, but after the rangers help with the cleanup, she realizes that reusing and recycling is much better than simply throwing away everything unwanted.

episodes.name: Rangers Raise a Condor
episodes.overview: Anna, B.B., and Lavender help a baby condor get back to its nest after it gets knocked out by a drone. The pilot is later revealed to be Patty Praxton, who wasn't being careful with the drone. The problem now is returning the baby to the nest... Without being near it.

episodes.name: Pony Party
episodes.overview: Anna, Pepper, and B.B. save a filly from a sandstorm and reunite it with her mother. After saving it, they find that the island's entire pony population ate the land clear of grass, and set off to find them a new home with plenty.

episodes.name: Land Ho
episodes.overview: Pepper, Indigo, and Anna save Preston and Patty from an ocean storm, discovering a new island in the process. Ufortunately, they are trapped by the Praxtons soon after, and quickly discover that the island house a very much active volcano.

episodes.name: The Strongest Spider
episodes.overview: Pepper, Mandy, and Lavender help a mama duck find her babies, but Lavender is afraid of spiders and refuses to be near one, causing many problems until they find help from one with super strong silk.

episodes.name: Rabbit Roundup
episodes.overview: Rosie, Lavender, and B.B. help remove invasive rabbits from Australian farm owned by Preston Praxton, who bought them as pets for his daughter Patty. Unfortunately, he refuses their help on a constant basis, and things get worse when Patty releases a European cat.

episodes.name: Uninvited Guest
episodes.overview: Rosie, Mandy, and Pepper have to help an alligator who has lost its home environment and ended up sleeping in Preston Praxton's swimming pool, but his trap ends up letting him and Patty set off the creature's ferocity with the rangers borderline helpless, even more so when they find out about his encroachment neighborhood.

episodes.name: Duck Duck Oops
episodes.overview: Pepper, Anna, and B.B. help ducks who are sinking in a rapidly draining pond, but after transferring them they find that Preston Praxton is draining all the ponds and lakes in the area to water a golf course, and he won't let anyone stop him.

episodes.name: Lost Island
episodes.overview: Rosie, Anna, and B.B. help a bunch of shrews find a new home after their island sinks underwater. The shrews, though, are determined to remain in their original home, but this only causes severe problems for everyone involved.

episodes.name: Flash Flood
episodes.overview: Rosie, Pepper, and Indigo help gorillas hit by a flash flood reunite somewhere safe, but the flood proves to be too dangerous and the gorillas are in further trouble, especially after one wrong throw sends them into the water.

episodes.name: Steer Me in the Right Direction
episodes.overview: Rosie, Indigo, and B.B. try to save a pair of cows from a wildfire. The only problem is the cows won't go towards the fire, and they resist almost every attempt the rangers make to save them, and Indigo is reluctant to accept help from cattle dogs.

episodes.name: The Case of the Missing Class Pet
episodes.overview: Indigo, Lavender, and B.B. try to save a missing class pet chameleon in a vacant lot near the school yard. Unfortunately, they find that the area is full of hungry raccoons, and the chameleon could be an easy snack

episodes.name: Bee Safe
episodes.overview: Lavender, B.B., and Anna help save a farm from crop-raiding elephants. They set off to take the elephants to an oasis, but the large mammals seem more willing to take the crops, forcing the others to think of a plan.

episodes.name: Chimp in Kaleidoscopia
episodes.overview: Anna, Pepper, and Indigo try to find a home for Earnest the circus chimpanzee. However, his human-raised background means he won't survive in the wild easily, and he is having problems learning the needed skills to live far from civilization. Additionally, he has instincts that prevent him from living with humans.

episodes.name: Pigeon Problems
episodes.overview: Lavender, Anna, and B.B. help a pigeon make a special delivery for his owner's granddaughter. They find out he is being confused by solar storms, and set off with him to help deliver his message.

episodes.name: Henpecked
episodes.overview: Rosie, Anna, and Lavender help a number of chickens that are severely stressed. They find that the chickens are having problems with their cramped spaces, and that Preston Praxton is the main cause to maximize profits, and he stubbornly refuses to give them more space.

episodes.name: Rangers in Space
episodes.overview: Rosie, B.B., and Indigo save a satellite from Preston and Patty's Space Shuttle, which is very poorly maintained and slowly falling apart. Unfortunately, Preston severely overestimates his shuttle's condition, and the rangers are forced to take drastic measures.

episodes.name: What a Gas
episodes.overview: Anna, B.B., and Lavender help cows that are wearing odd tanks to collect their burps. Upon removing them, they find that Preston Praxton created the tanks to provide power to his farm with methane emissions from cow burps, and he won't see the rangers' side of the argument.

episodes.name: Turtle Trek
episodes.overview: Rosie, Mandy, and B.B. help a baby sea turtle find his way to the ocean after it follows the light of Preston Praxton's beach estate instead of that from the moon. Unfortunately, their attempts are constantly thwarted by nature.

episodes.name: Tornado Hunters
episodes.overview: Anna, Lavender, and B.B. try to save Preston and Patty from a tornado while the Praxtons are chasing storms. Preston in particular is willing to ignore all safety precautions about tornados just for the sake of the perfect pictures, and he refuses to get to safety, endangering himself and everyone else.

episodes.name: The Air Up There
episodes.overview: B.B., Indigo, and Lavender try to clear the air of a polluted city so that everyone can breathe properly. The culprit turns out to be Preston Praxton, and he consistently denies the pollution is even existing.

episodes.name: Dust in the Wind
episodes.overview: Rosie, Indigo, and B.B. save a family of javelinas from an intense desert dust storm. After reuniting them, the group now have to find them a safe place in the storm, but the storm's strong winds make staying inside very tricky.

episodes.name: Catch a Tiger
episodes.overview: Anna, Pepper, and B.B. help save a tiger thought to be extinct from a booby trap set by Preston Praxton, who plans on using him for publicity purposes. Unfortunately, the tiger cannot understand Anna and Preston is determined to keep him, making a large amount of difficulty for the mission.

episodes.name: A Hot Topic
episodes.overview: Anna, B.B., and Lavender help to save the unique animals at a hydrothermal vent threatened by an undersea mining operation. After helping a white octopus from a rockslide, they have to deal with a blocked vent, but not all of the animals can move to a new home.

episodes.name: Giant Catfish
episodes.overview: Anna, B.B., and Pepper rescue a giant catfish stuck in shallow waters full of litter. Unfortunately, its gargantuan size and weight makes moving it extremely difficult for the rangers.

episodes.name: Prairie Dog Day Afternoon
episodes.overview: B.B., Rosie, and Indigo try to save some prairie dogs, a keystone species, after Patty Praxton paves over their burrows and traps them under a large expanse of concrete meant for a skate park. To make matters worse, Indigo is more focused on skating and she ends up making the problem worse when it turns out she is covering more than just prairie dog burrows.

episodes.name: We Didn't Start the Fire Ants
episodes.overview: B.B., Indigo, and Lavender help a little kangaroo who is stung by invasive fire ants. Kangaroo healed, they now have to get the fire ants back to South America- a much more difficult tasked than originally planned.

episodes.name: Look Out Lemur
episodes.overview: Mandy, Pepper, and Indigo help a baby ring-tailed lemur who is caught in a flash flood. After saving him from the water, they now have to find a way to convince Preston Praxton to change how he is farming to stop erosion- which is easier said than done.

episodes.name: Don't Move a Mussel
episodes.overview: Anna, B.B., and Indigo must round up invasive zebra mussels that Preston Praxton brought to Okanagan Lake irresponsibly from the Great Lakes after breaking regulations in boating. The group has to stop Preston's carelessness before he can potentially harm the Ogopogo.

episodes.name: Praxton Islands, Inc.
episodes.overview: Rosie, B.B., and Anna deal with issues from the construction of artificial islands created by Preston Praxton as a part of a long scheme of attracting potential vacationers. The process is kicking up a lot of silt, but Praxton won't see the damage he's doing.

episodes.name: Get the Lead Out
episodes.overview: B.B., Lavender, and Indigo save a family and their neighbors from lead in their home water supply. The underground pipes in the have been found to be corroded, and the rangers must hurry before the problem gets worse.

episodes.name: The Tortoise and the Heiress
episodes.overview: Indigo, Rosie, and B.B. help free a tortoise from rocks after being buried by careless driving on the Praxtons' part. Preston refuses to abide by the rules already set, forcing the rangers to be creative in their approach.

episodes.name: Getting Swampy
episodes.overview: Rosie, Mandy, and Pepper help put out a fire in a colony of orangutans' home near a swamp. The team then discovers that the fires were caused by peat embers and the swamp is almost practically dry, as Preston Praxton built an abandoned canal for logging purposes.

episodes.name: The Otter and the Oil
episodes.overview: Indigo, Lavender, and B.B. have to save an otter from an oil slick, and its cleanup proves to be very tricky and messy.

episodes.name: Icebreakers
episodes.overview: Indigo, Mandy, and Rosie have to save a pod of orcas trapped in ice at the frozen north of the arctic ocean. The problem is that every attempt is thwarted by the freezing water, and the hole only gets smaller as time grows on.

episodes.name: Coral Calamity
episodes.overview: Rosie, Anna, and B.B. save a coral reef from losing its color after Preston Praxton carelessly prances around on them not knowing coral is alive. The hard part is letting him know the truth, and he refuses to believe that coral can live

episodes.name: S'no Problem
episodes.overview: Rosie, B.B., and Indigo save Patty and Preston from an avalanche while the 2 are enjoying the snowy weather on a mountain. While Patty listens closely to the rangers, Preston is much less cooperative and threatens to put everyone at risk with his carelessness.

episodes.name: A Whale of a Problem
episodes.overview: Rosie, B.B., and Mandy have to save a whale who is beached on the shore, but no matter how many times Rosie sends him back in the sea, the whale always ends up back on dry land. They eventually find that the whale is scared by Preston's submarine sonar and he won't believe their words and refuses to shut off the sonar.

episodes.name: Bee Like Lavender
episodes.overview: B.B., Indigo, and Lavender have to save sick bees and an apple orchard from Preston's pesticides. In addition to trying to stop Preston, the group also have to convince Lavender to help out, as she is very scared of bees.

episodes.name: Monkey Business
episodes.overview: The Rangers have to save a pygmy marmoset that Preston has captured as a pet for Patty, but the only problem is that the marmoset has no intention of living in captivity, and the Praxtons are not willing to give him up.

episodes.name: Lost Panda Cub
episodes.overview: B.B., Lavender, and Mandy have to help a lost panda cub get home. The problem is that they can't let him see them, and a snow leopard is stalking them to try an get a meal.

episodes.name: Divided We Fall
episodes.overview: Anna, Rosie, and B.B. save an elephant family from a Poacher determined to take the mother's tusks, but the group is divided when Anna prioritizes the baby while the others go for the mother, landing the mission at extreme risk.

episodes.name: White-Nosed Bats
episodes.overview: Rosie, Mandy, and B.B. try to help a horse escape constant agonizing bites from several mosquitoes. Coming to the conclusion that there are too many insects due to there being no bats around to eat them, Rosie refuses to look for them, being severely afraid of bats. Things get complicated when they find out the bats have white nose disease, and Rosie is refusing to touch them.

episodes.name: The Earth Needs Their Kelp
episodes.overview: Rosie, B.B. and Indigo must return balance to an ocean environment.

episodes.name: Iceberg Ahead
episodes.overview: A large iceberg calves, leaving a floe on a collision course for a clan of polar bears. Anna, Indigo, and Rosie must save them.

episodes.name: Backyard Bird Feeder
episodes.overview: Patty's backyard feeder is too close to a glass window, and Anna, Lavender and B.B. need to find another way to safely feed the birds.

episodes.name: If You Can't Stand the Heat
episodes.overview: When Rosie, B.B. and Mandy act to save animals from a forest fire, they jump the gun and accidentally put out a controlled burn.

episodes.name: Moo-ving Cows
episodes.overview: Rosie, Pepper and Mandy have to stop Preston Praxton from poisoning a stream with pesticides.

episodes.name: Panda-monium
episodes.overview: Anna, Indigo and Rosie work to reunite and relocate a family of pandas when their home environment is destroyed.

episodes.name: The Big Dig
episodes.overview: Rosie, Anna and B.B. discover that Preston Praxton has been causing earthquakes by digging underground.

episodes.name: Catalog Slog
episodes.overview: Preston sends out big, thick catalogs that overflow landfills and Rosie, Pepper and Lavender must stop him.

episodes.name: Preston Fest
episodes.overview: Preston throws a music festival that destroys all the local vegetation, threatening local wildlife who are now going hungry and Mandy, B.B. and Lavender have to do something.

episodes.name: Snakes on a Plain
episodes.overview: Rosie, Mandy and Anna help protect the lives of snakes during their migration.

episodes.name: Big Gold Superbloom
episodes.overview: Wildflowers are being destroyed, causing tomato worms to devour the crops on a nearby farm. Anna, Indigo and Lavender must save the day.

episodes.name: Batter Up
episodes.overview: B.B., Indigo and Lavender need to help bats from colliding with wind turbines.

episodes.name: Missed Them by a Hare
episodes.overview: Climate change causes snow to melt prematurely, leaving a family of snow hares vulnerable to predators. Anna, Rosie and Pepper must protect them.

episodes.name: Drone Zone
episodes.overview: B.B., Lavender and Pepper attempt to save a bear cub stuck on the side of a mountain.

episodes.name: Marshland Chronicles
episodes.overview: A spring morning snowstorm is followed by an abrupt afternoon warm-up, causing a flood of melted snow that threatens the local wildlife.

episodes.name: Otterly Lost
episodes.overview: An otter loses her favorite rock.

episodes.name: Tigertastic
episodes.overview: Preston destroys mangrove forests in India to create profitable shrimp farms, exposing the area and its wildlife to storms, and Pepper, Indigo, and Lavender must do something to stop him

episodes.name: Seal Gone Wild
episodes.overview: Mandy, B.B., and Lavender have to get a lost seal back home after it wreaks havoc on a city.

episodes.name: Chimney Caper
episodes.overview: During the holidays, Rosie, B.B and Lavender need to remove a raccoon family looking for warmth that becomes trapped in Preston's chimney.

episodes.name: Smuggle a Snuggle
episodes.overview: Patty smuggles sugar gliders into the country to give as "party favors" at her birthday party and Anna, Indigo and Lavender need to do something.

episodes.name: Frozen Falls
episodes.overview: Rosie, Mandy, and B.B. save turtles trapped on an ice floe when a waterfall freezes over, but their save has consequences.

episodes.name: Got Silk?
episodes.overview: Lavender, Indigo, and Pepper save spiders from the Praxtons, who are silking them for their silk.

episodes.name: Flyaway
episodes.overview: The Praxtons use helium balloons to try and set a world record, so Rosie, Mandy and Lavender must stop them.

episodes.name: Safari Soulmates
episodes.overview: In Africa, the symbiotic relationship between ostriches and zebras is threatened when Preston rounds up ostriches for his own profit. So Anna, Pepper and Indigo must stop him.

episodes.name: Spooky Costume Party
episodes.overview: B.B., Lavender, and Mandy help Patty with an eco-friendly spooky costume party.

episodes.name: GMO OMG
episodes.overview: Mandy, Anna and B.B. rescue the city of the plant have got power Preston's genetically modified crops are going crazy.

episodes.name: The Lost Puppy
episodes.overview: Rosie, Anna and Pepper save a lost puppy that is stuck in a city sewer system.

episodes.name: Goats in Trees
episodes.overview: Priscilla Praxton removes pesky seed-spitting tree goats from her orchard. Mandy, Anna and Pepper must save these goats.

episodes.name: Team Rainbow Rangers!
episodes.overview: Pepper, Indigo, and Lavender have to stop a factory from pouring rainbow color in the river.

episodes.name: Wingin' It
episodes.overview: Lavender, Anna, and B.B. help a physically challenged duckling fly, so it can catch up to its migrating flock.

episodes.name: Whale of a Tale
episodes.overview: When heavy boat traffic disrupts a migrating whale and her calf, Anna, B.B., and Mandy must keep them safe.

episodes.name: Construction Destruction
episodes.overview: Indigo, Anna, and Pepper save a coral reef from being damaged by a reckless construction team.

episodes.name: Chimp in the Wild
episodes.overview: Anna, Pepper, and Indigo check whether their chimpanzee friend Ernest is ready to return to the wild.

episodes.name: Shake It
episodes.overview: After a terrible earthquake, Mandy, Pepper, and Lavender try to save a group of ducks.

episodes.name: Gold in That Thar Moon
episodes.overview: Preston's gold mining mission on the Moon is endangering gorillas on Earth, and the Rosie, B.B. and Indigo must stop him.

episodes.name: Gem of a Friend
episodes.overview: Rosie, B.B. and Anna must save Floof after Preston captures him.

episodes.name: Bunny Buddies
episodes.overview: Mandy, B.B., and Lavender save pet bunnies that have been let out into the wild.

episodes.name: I Wasn't Borneo Yesterday
episodes.overview: Rosie, Mandy, and Pepper work to solve problems with a palm oil plantation.

episodes.name: Teacup Tigers
episodes.overview: Anna, Pepper, and B.B. save tigers from Preston who is trying to catch them for Patty's tea party.

episodes.name: Glass Warfare
episodes.overview: When Priscilla turns a desert into glass and creates sandstorms, Rosie, Indigo, and B.B. have to stop her.

episodes.name: Who Said Bat
episodes.overview: B.B, Indigo and Lavender need to help bats from flying into wind turbines.

episodes.name: What's Mine is Mine
episodes.overview: Pollution from a gold mine threatens the otters in the ocean.

episodes.name: Green is the New Black
episodes.overview: Microfibers from Preston's new fashion line causes environmental problems in the ocean. But Rosie, Pepper and Lavender have to stop him.

episodes.name: Plastic Bottle Island
episodes.overview: A bottle-nosed dolphin gets a plastic six-pack ring stuck on its nose and mouth. But Mandy, Indigo and B.B they have to cleaning.

episodes.name: Calling Fowl
episodes.overview: Pepper, Anna, and B.B. discover Preston Praxton is feeding ducks to keep them off his golf course.

episodes.name: Treehouse Trouble
episodes.overview: Preston is harvesting trees so Patty can build her massive dream treehouse, but it destroying the forest. But Rosie, B.B. and Lavender are sent to stop him.

episodes.name: Car Wash
episodes.overview: Preston is washing his car in his orchard. The runoff from the chemicals in the soap is polluting the riverbed and harming animals, so Rosie, Pepper, and Mandy are sent to fix this.

episodes.name: Preston's Shipwreck
episodes.overview: Preston's determination to find treasure in a pirate shipwreck threatens an inter-marine-species, so Rosie, Anna, and B.B. are sent to stop him.

episodes.name: Wild, Wild Horses
episodes.overview: Preston's latest get-rich-quick scheme to sell wild mustangs goes awry when Anna, Pepper, and B.B. set out to reunite them

episodes.name: Safari Away from Me
episodes.overview: A man causes a baby elephant to become separated from her mother, Anna, Rosie and B.B. set out to stop him.

episodes.name: Bunny-20
episodes.overview: Kalia sends all The Rainbow Rangers to find a cure for all the sick bunnies.

episodes.name: Croaking In The Rain/Hoots on First
Why So Crabby?/Surprise! It's A... Forest Fire
